Topical news show hosted by comedian Russell Howard, who offers his unique and quirky take on the week's global headlines and bizarre news stories.

[img]http://extraimago.com/images/2015/10/30/341514006b0f07732540385ecf3ecf03.jpg[/img]

Russell Howards returns to offer his unique take on the week's global headlines and bizarre news stories. Sifting through over 60 international news channels, 140 newspapers from around the world and over a thousand news clips, no stone is left unturned in his pursuit of the weird and wonderful stories that have been dominating the press and TV news. As well as his trademark mix of topical stand-up and sketches, not to mention the inspirational and thought-provoking story to close the show on a feelgood note, Russell will also chat to a high-profile person involved in the news that week
